        Constructor for an order with shed

        Parameters:
        depth - The depth of the carport in cm
        height - The depth of the carport in cm
        width - The width of the carport in cm
        shedDepth - The depth of the shed in cm
        shedWidth - The width of the shed in cm
        incline - How much incline the roof has. (0 = flat roof)
        withShed - Whether or not the order has a shed
        customer - The customer connected with the order
